<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading" lang="en">Medical Research Council (United Kingdom)</h1>			<div id="bodyContent" class="mw-body-content">
				<div id="siteSub" class="noprint">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</div>				<div id="contentSub"><span class="mw-redirectedfrom">&#160;&#160;(Redirected from <a href="/w/index.php?title=Medical_Research_Council_(UK)&amp;redirect=no" class="mw-redirect" title="Medical Research Council (UK)">Medical Research Council (UK)</a>)</span></div>
				<div id="jump-to-nav"></div>				<a class="mw-jump-link" href="#mw-head">Jump to navigation</a>
				<a class="mw-jump-link" href="#p-search">Jump to search</a>
				<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="mw-parser-output"><p class="mw-empty-elt">

</p>
<table class="infobox vcard" style="width:22em"><caption class="fn org">Medical Research Council</caption><tbody><tr><td colspan="2" style="text-align:center"><a href="/wiki/File:UK_Medical_Research_Council_Logo.jpg" class="image"><img alt="UK Medical Research Council Logo.jpg" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/e/e2/UK_Medical_Research_Council_Logo.jpg/230px-UK_Medical_Research_Council_Logo.jpg" decoding="async" width="230" height="102" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/e/e2/UK_Medical_Research_Council_Logo.jpg/345px-UK_Medical_Research_Council_Logo.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/e/e2/UK_Medical_Research_Council_Logo.jpg/460px-UK_Medical_Research_Council_Logo.jpg 2x" data-file-width="474" data-file-height="210" /></a></td></tr><tr><th scope="row" style="padding-right:0.6em;">Abbreviation</th><td class="nickname">MRC</td></tr><tr><th scope="row" style="padding-right:0.6em;">Formation</th><td class="note">1913</td></tr><tr><th scope="row" style="padding-right:0.6em;">Type</th><td><a href="/wiki/Non-departmental_public_body" title="Non-departmental public body">Non-Departmental Government Body</a></td></tr><tr><th scope="row" style="padding-right:0.6em;">Purpose</th><td>Co-ordinating and funding medical research in the United Kingdom</td></tr><tr><th scope="row" style="padding-right:0.6em;">Location</th><td class="label"><div class="plainlist"><ul><li>Medical Research Council<br />
